#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.f1_score.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.f1\\_score"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:1 of
msgid "Compute the F1 score, also known as balanced F-score or F-measure"
msgstr "计算 F1 分数，也称为平衡 F 分数或 F 度量"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:3 of
msgid ""
"The F1 score can be interpreted as a weighted average of the precision "
"and recall, where an F1 score reaches its best value at 1 and worst score"
" at 0. The relative contribution of precision and recall to the F1 score "
"are equal. The formula for the F1 score is::"
msgstr ""
"F1 分数可以解释为精确率和召回率的加权平均值，其中 F1 分数的最佳值为 1，最"
"差值为 0。精确率和召回率对 F1 分数的相对贡献相等。F1 分数的公式为："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:10 of
msgid ""
"In the multi-class and multi-label case, this is the average of the F1 "
"score of each class with weighting depending on the ``average`` "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"在多类和多标签情况下，这是每个类别的 F1 分数的平均值，其权重取决于 ``"
"average`` 参数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:14 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参阅 :ref:`用户指南 <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:16 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:18 of
msgid "Estimated targets as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "由分类器返回的预测目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:20 of
msgid ""
"The set of labels to include when ``average != 'binary'``, and their "
"order if ``average is None``. Labels present in the data can be excluded,"
" for example to calculate a multiclass average ignoring a majority "
"negative class, while labels not present in the data will result in 0 "
"components in a macro average. For multilabel targets, labels are column "
"indices. By default, all labels in ``y_true`` and ``y_pred`` are used in "
"sorted order."
msgstr ""
"当 ``average != 'binary'`` 时要包含的标签集合，以及当 ``average is None``"
" 时它们的顺序。数据中存在的标签可以被排除，例如在计算多类平均值时忽略多数"
"负类，而数据中不存在的标签将在宏平均中导致 0 组件。对于多标签目标，标签是"
"列索引。默认情况下，将使用 ``y_true`` 和 ``y_pred`` 中的所有标签并按排序"
"顺序排列。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:28 of
msgid ""
"The class to report if ``average='binary'`` and the data is binary. If "
"the data are multiclass or multilabel, this will be ignored; setting "
"``labels=[pos_label]`` and ``average != 'binary'`` will report scores for"
" that label only."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``average='binary'`` 且数据是二分类的，则报告该类别。如果数据是多类"
"或多标签的，则此参数将被忽略；设置 ``labels=[pos_label]`` 且 ``average !="
" 'binary'`` 将仅报告该标签的分数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:33 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:  ``'binary'``:"
"     Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``.     "
"This is applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary. "
"``'micro'``:     Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true "
"positives,     false negatives and false positives. ``'macro'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted     mean.  "
"This does not take label imbalance into account. ``'weighted'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted     by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This     alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an     F-score "
"that is not between precision and recall. ``'samples'``:     Calculate "
"metrics for each instance, and find their average (only     meaningful "
"for multilabel classification where this differs from     "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""
"此参数对于多类/多标签目标是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类别的分数"
"。否则，此参数决定对数据执行的平均类型：``'binary'``：     仅报告由 ``pos"
"_label`` 指定的类别的结果。     此选项仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``）是"
"二分类的情况。 ``'micro'``：     通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例全局"
"计算指标。 ``'macro'``：     计算每个标签的指标，并求其未加权平均值。这不"
"考虑标签不平衡。 ``'weighted'``：     计算每个标签的指标，并按支持度（"
"每个标签的真正例数）加权平均。这会调整 “macro” 以考虑标签不平衡；它可能"
"导致 F 分数不在精确率和召回率之间。 ``'samples'``：     计算每个实例的"
"指标，并求其平均值（仅在多标签分类中与 :func:`accuracy_score` 不同时有"
"意义）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:33 of
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:"
msgstr ""
"此参数对于多类/多标签目标是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类的分数。"
"否则，这将确定对数据执行的平均类型："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:37 of
msgid "``'binary'``:"
msgstr "``'binary'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:38 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``. This is "
"applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary."
msgstr ""
"仅报告由 ``pos_label`` 指定的类的结果。这仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``"
"）为二进制的情况。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:40 of
msgid "``'micro'``:"
msgstr "``'micro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:41 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true positives, false "
"negatives and false positives."
msgstr "通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例来全局计算指标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:43 of
msgid "``'macro'``:"
msgstr "``'macro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:44 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted mean.  This "
"does not take label imbalance into account."
msgstr "计算每个标签的指标，并找到它们的未加权平均值。这不考虑标签不平衡。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:46 of
msgid "``'weighted'``:"
msgstr "``'weighted'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:47 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an F-score that "
"is not between precision and recall."
msgstr ""
"计算每个标签的指标，并找到它们的加权平均值（权重为支持度，即每个标签的"
"真实实例数）。这会修改 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；可能导致 F 分数不在精确"
"率和召回率之间。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:51 of
msgid "``'samples'``:"
msgstr "``'samples'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:52 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each instance, and find their average (only "
"meaningful for multilabel classification where this differs from "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:56 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:58 of
msgid ""
"Sets the value to return when there is a zero division, i.e. when all "
"predictions and labels are negative. If set to \"warn\", this acts as 0, "
"but warnings are also raised."
msgstr ""
"设置在零除法时返回的值，即所有预测和标签均为负时的情况。如果设置为 \"warn"
"\"，则其作用为 0，但也会引发警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:63 of
msgid ""
"**f1_score** -- F1 score of the positive class in binary classification "
"or weighted average of the F1 scores of each class for the multiclass "
"task."
msgstr ""
"**f1_score** -- 在二分类任务中为正类的 F1 分数，或多类任务中每个类别的 F1"
" 分数的加权平均值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.f1_score:67 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`fbeta_score`, :py:obj:`precision_recall_fscore_support`, "
":py:obj:`jaccard_score`, :py:obj:`multilabel_confusion_matrix`"
msgstr ""

